<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>RoleRocket Resume</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family:Calibri,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;line-height:1.55;color:#1f2937;margin:0;padding:20px;">
    
    <div style="font-family:Calibri,Arial,sans-serif;color:#1f2937;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="border-bottom:3px solid #1e3a56;padding-bottom:10px;margin-bottom:14px;">
        <div style="font-size:24pt;font-weight:700;color:#1e3a56;line-height:1.1;">John Brown</div>
        <div style="font-size:11pt;color:#475569;margin-top:6px;">Contact:</div>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:11pt;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 14px 0;"><strong>Target Role:</strong> Customer Service Representative</div>
      <div style="margin:0 0 14px 0;">
        <div style="font-size:12.5pt;font-weight:700;color:#1e3a56;margin-bottom:6px;">Professional Summary</div>
        <p style="margin:0;line-height:1.55;color:#1f2937;">Dedicated Customer Service Representative with a Bachelor’s degree in Management Studies and a Certified Customer Service Professional designation. Proven ability to handle high volumes of customer queries and enhance customer satisfaction. Committed to delivering exceptional service and fostering positive relationships with clients.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin:0 0 14px 0;">
        <div style="font-size:12.5pt;font-weight:700;color:#1e3a56;margin-bottom:6px;">Experience</div>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.55;color:#1f2937;"><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Managed and resolved an average of 90 customer queries daily, ensuring timely and effective solutions.</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Improved Customer Satisfaction (CSAT) scores by 20% through proactive communication and problem-solving techniques.</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Collaborated with team members to streamline processes and enhance overall service delivery.</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Utilized CRM software to track customer interactions and follow up on unresolved issues.</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="margin:0 0 14px 0;">
        <div style="font-size:12.5pt;font-weight:700;color:#1e3a56;margin-bottom:6px;">Education</div>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.55;color:#1f2937;"><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">BSc in Management Studies, University of the West Indies (UWI), 2021</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="margin:0 0 14px 0;">
        <div style="font-size:12.5pt;font-weight:700;color:#1e3a56;margin-bottom:6px;">Certifications</div>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.55;color:#1f2937;"><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Certified Customer Service Professional, 2023</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="margin:0;">
        <div style="font-size:12.5pt;font-weight:700;color:#1e3a56;margin-bottom:6px;">Skills</div>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.55;color:#1f2937;"><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Excellent verbal and written communication</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Strong problem-solving abilities</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Proficient in CRM software</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Customer relationship management</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Time management and multitasking</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Team collaboration and support</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Adaptability to changing environments</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Conflict resolution techniques</li><li style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">Reply EDIT + what to change, or reply 1 for job matches.</li></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  
  </body>
</html>